  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/242212.htm", 
  "description": "<p><strong>国际直线对撞机是一台价值数十亿美元超高能量正负电子对撞机，它由2个大型超导直线加速器组成，可将电子和正电子加速至光速，能量达到5000亿电子伏特，并具有升级至1万亿电子伏特的潜力。</strong>该仪器宽度为39英尺，是国际直线对撞机三台大型探测器之一，使用粒子流热量测定法测量来自电子和正电子碰撞时产生的能量释放。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2dafff66/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242212.htm&amp;t=%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%88%96%E6%89%BF%E5%BB%BA5000%E4%BA%BF%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E4%BC%8F%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E8%B6%85%E7%BA%A7%E7%9B%B4%E7%BA%BF%E5%AF%B9%E6%92%9E%E6%9C%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242212.htm&amp;t=%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%88%96%E6%89%BF%E5%BB%BA5000%E4%BA%BF%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E4%BC%8F%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E8%B6%85%E7%BA%A7%E7%9B%B4%E7%BA%BF%E5%AF%B9%E6%92%9E%E6%9C%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242212.htm&amp;t=%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%88%96%E6%89%BF%E5%BB%BA5000%E4%BA%BF%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E4%BC%8F%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E8%B6%85%E7%BA%A7%E7%9B%B4%E7%BA%BF%E5%AF%B9%E6%92%9E%E6%9C%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242212.htm&amp;t=%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%88%96%E6%89%BF%E5%BB%BA5000%E4%BA%BF%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E4%BC%8F%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E8%B6%85%E7%BA%A7%E7%9B%B4%E7%BA%BF%E5%AF%B9%E6%92%9E%E6%9C%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.